  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=328">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=328">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Vampiric Embrace was recently upgraded with the patch as of 5/19/99.  It drains life from other creatures and adds it to the characters own.  The apparent formula is <level>*2+2 HP drained per use.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>None<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    HP drain on mob, Add HP to you.
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
