			I have found that as I gain levels, the spell works more frequently. I am at Lvl 15 now, and the last 5 times I've used it, it has worked in every fight but one, and during the last fight, it kicked in 4 times in a row!! That's 4x27HP plus whatever damage my weap does, (12-19 usually)!<BR>
<BR>
I now cast it every time I melee, since it now costs me less than 1/2 a bubble to cast.<BR>
<BR>
I have done lots of experimenting, and it does not seem to matter whether or not you are armed, for the spell to work. In the details above, I was using my Great Staff, fighting in UnRest. I have also used my Daggar with similar results. Unless I read somewhere that no weapons at all make it more affective, you won't see me trying that...<BR>
