	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			I just got vampiric embrace; as a 9th level necro, I've found this is an incredible spell. Its limitations are interesting, and I can see why people have trouble making it work. Here is what I've discovered:<BR>
<BR>
What weapon you use does not matter.<BR>
<BR>
You have to be at touch range to the creature--just because you're close enough for your weapon to hit the creature does not mean you're close enough to vampiric embrace the creature.<BR>
<BR>
If you're moving when the vampiric embrace goes off, it gets interrupted.<BR>
<BR>
I generally get 2 or 3 off per combat, and at level 8 I've been solo-ing young kodiaks that con red.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
